            <title><![CDATA[[Life]  방통대 첫 기말고사 완료]]></title>
            <link>https://www.ryoonwithwisdomtrees.world/article/general-records/2024-06-08-thelog</link>
            <guid>https://www.ryoonwithwisdomtrees.world/article/general-records/2024-06-08-thelog</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="notion-article" class="mx-auto overflow-hidden "><main class="notion light-mode notion-page notion-block-1341eb5c0337814a97a2dde21030aec0"><div class="notion-viewport"></div><div class="notion-collection-page-properties"><div class="notion-collection-row"><div class="notion-collection-row-body"></div></div></div><div class="notion-text notion-block-1341eb5c03378123b550e3f4a675e423">방통대 첫 학기 기말고사를 치르고 집으로 돌아가는 길. 햇빛으로 쨍-한 하늘이 온통 눈부시던 날이었던지라 일부러 집에서 조금은 거리가 먼 버스 정류장에 내렸다. 내려가는 길 성당이 보이길래 잠시 들렀다.</div><div class="notion-blank notion-block-1341eb5c033781afbb9cd56af4a5063c"> </div><div class="notion-blank notion-block-1341eb5c03378179b634f85e2b04e1d0"> </div><figure class="notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-1341eb5c0337811db04acb4776a4c427"><div style="position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F056ff9f5-a9ef-486f-8acb-9eef51d06a2d%2Fec40668f-eb62-4a16-a22f-58a86c533781%2FIMG_7003.jpeg?table=block&amp;id=1341eb5c-0337-811d-b04a-cb4776a4c427&amp;t=1341eb5c-0337-811d-b04a-cb4776a4c427" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><figure class="notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-1341eb5c0337812c807aff54ac05d6e8"><div style="position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F056ff9f5-a9ef-486f-8acb-9eef51d06a2d%2F3b576753-c273-474c-bf2e-1c61101ce178%2FIMG_7004.jpeg?table=block&amp;id=1341eb5c-0337-812c-807a-ff54ac05d6e8&amp;t=1341eb5c-0337-812c-807a-ff54ac05d6e8" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><div class="notion-blank notion-block-1341eb5c033781479737f5805609e4cb"> </div><div class="notion-text notion-block-1341eb5c033781e78d6ed880bf458931">아무도 없는 조용한 오후 4시 쯤의 성당.</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-1341eb5c033781fcb2cbef241e31b949">전체를 차지하는 것 같이 누릴 수 있었던 기도의 시간과 은총. 기도드린바 대로 나 자신이 이루어 보자. 이루어 주자.</div><div class="notion-blank notion-block-1341eb5c03378171aff0d6edd50d717a"> </div></main></div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
