ter;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F056ff9f5-a9ef-486f-8acb-9eef51d06a2d%2Ffa2418f5-831b-4903-a6eb-d5c5229d5581%2F%25E1%2584%2589%25E1%2585%25B3%25E1%2584%258F%25E1%2585%25B3%25E1%2584%2585%25E1%2585%25B5%25E1%2586%25AB%25E1%2584%2589%25E1%2585%25A3%25E1%2586%25BA_2024-06-14_%25E1%2584%258B%25E1%2585%25A9%25E1%2584%2592%25E1%2585%25AE_8.24.24.png?table=block&amp;id=1341eb5c-0337-81b5-9c12-c73a10c1ebab&amp;t=1341eb5c-0337-81b5-9c12-c73a10c1ebab" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><figure class="notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-1341eb5c033781aa9bace10e0aff578e"><div style="position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F056ff9f5-a9ef-486f-8acb-9eef51d06a2d%2Ff34ce597-1355-4736-9df6-6d85c2671298%2F%25E1%2584%2589%25E1%2585%25B3%25E1%2584%258F%25E1%2585%25B3%25E1%2584%2585%25E1%2585%25B5%25E1%2586%25AB%25E1%2584%2589%25E1%2585%25A3%25E1%2586%25BA_2024-06-14_%25E1%2584%258B%25E1%2585%25A9%25E1%2584%2592%25E1%2585%25AE_8.24.30.png?table=block&amp;id=1341eb5c-0337-81aa-9bac-e10e0aff578e&amp;t=1341eb5c-0337-81aa-9bac-e10e0aff578e" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><figure class="notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-1341eb5c0337819382ebfae57da38d79"><div style="position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F056ff9f5-a9ef-486f-8acb-9eef51d06a2d%2Fe5915d71-9bd4-4ca2-a866-88c37c97f4df%2F%25E1%2584%2589%25E1%2585%25B3%25E1%2584%258F%25E1%2585%25B3%25E1%2584%2585%25E1%2585%25B5%25E1%2586%25AB%25E1%2584%2589%25E1%2585%25A3%25E1%2586%25BA_2024-06-14_%25E1%2584%258B%25E1%2585%25A9%25E1%2584%2592%25E1%2585%25AE_8.24.34.png?table=block&amp;id=1341eb5c-0337-8193-82eb-fae57da38d79&amp;t=1341eb5c-0337-8193-82eb-fae57da38d79" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><div class="notion-text notion-block-1341eb5c033781ccb98ceaabc4396a7a">

아무튼. 책이건, 대화건, 경험이건 어떤 루트를 통해 배우더라도 그 배움의 슬픔과 기쁨이 나를 오늘과 내일로 걸어나갈 수 있게 한다는 점에서 배움은 영원한 것이다.

나이 들수록 배울 수 있어서 좋고 배우는 것 자체가 즐겁다. 특히나 능력뿐만 아니라 역량이 점점 더 부각되는 시대를 살아가고 있기도 하니까.</div></main></div>]]></content:encoded>
